data.title: Sophie Amalie of Brunswick-Lüneburg, Queen consort of Denmark and Norway
data.text:
Birth24.3.1628 in Herzberg Castle, Lower SaxonyDeath20.2.1685 in Amalienborg Palace, Copenhagen, Denmark (56 years) MarriageKing Frederik III of Denmark and Norway

Wedding: 1.10.1643 in Schloss GlücksburgChildrenKing Christian V of Denmark and Norway

Princess Anna Sophie of Denmark and Norway, Electress consort of Saxony
